race.comment: KNOW THYSELF (3) exciting gelding who won The Coast last May defeating Depth Of Character and Mare Of Mount Buller when sitting on the speed. Undefeated in three second-up runs and he gets the right setup today as he gets to his preferred distance. Hard to stop. COLLECT YOUR CASH (10) will push forward and comes here in peak condition fourth-up. Drops in weight and brings the right profile in this tougher contest. Each way. MARE OF MT BULLER (7) three weeks between runs when she rounded them up with ease over 1600m at Randwick. Will be snagged back from the draw and be saved for one final crack at them. Keep safe. SUN GOD (12) deep into the prep and don't let him slip under the guard. Raced without luck when fourth in the small field over 1600m at Randwick. No shock to see him finish over the top of these. AMOR VICTORIOUS (2) comes back from Queensland after scoring a gritty win in the LR Members Mile at Eagle Farm. Stays in the mix.
